        <h3>What is Diamond?</h3>
        <p>
            Diamonds are the result of carbon being exposed to extreme heat and pressure deep within the earth. This gemstone is often used to make a variety of different types of jewelry because of its sparkle and exceptional durability.
        </p>
    </section>

