                <h3>Cut:</h3>
                <p>Appearance and how well it interacts with light.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Clarity:</h3>
                <p>The smaller the amount of internal impurities and external trace defects, the more valuable it is.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Color:</h3>
                <p>The whiter the color of the diamond, the higher its value.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Carat:</h3>
                <p>Weight of the diamond.</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>

